        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[UST办事攻略]]></title>
            <link>undefined/posts/UST办事攻略</link>
            <guid>undefined/posts/UST办事攻略</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 12:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="重要链接" tabindex="-1">重要链接 <a class="header-anchor" href="#重要链接" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;重要链接&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<h3 id="教学侧" tabindex="-1">教学侧 <a class="header-anchor" href="#教学侧" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;教学侧&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h3>
<ol>
<li>
<p><strong>CES的UG教育网站</strong>提供了有关课程描述、学制要求和学习道路的详细信息：<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/ugeducation/#/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">CES的UG教育网站</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>课程详情</strong>可以在以下链接查看：<a href="https://w5.hkust-gz.edu.cn/wcq/cgi-bin/2330/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">课程详情链接</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>UG课程介绍、通用课程与基础课程</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/ugeducation/#/UC/#/courses" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">UG课程介绍</a></li>
<li><a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/ugeducation/#/UC/#/common" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">通用课程</a></li>
<li><a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/ugeducation/#/UC/#/education" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">基础课程</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>专业课程要求</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>人工智能专业课程要求：<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/general/index/show_file/file_id/OTRkZkozbVNOdmQ5Y05DK3IvMzRIbVM0Vk5GeHAvVFBOT2ZNdjFmQWhSV2lUSncrWWo0UkF5VW9zcS9nb25xa1dYU0pLOWtjdVZKb0t2K0ExUQ==" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">人工智能专业课程要求</a>和<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/general/index/show_file/file_id/YzNmMjlneDA5Z01IK2RObkNjZEdNT1Bjc2ErcHo2UEpxSEVMbFRVRGVCaDFOK3k0cjJldEhjYnhuckZzSnZESTRUa2RJWlowNW9vdzk0N1R4QQ==" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">路径</a>。</li>
<li>数据科学和大数据技术专业课程要求：<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/general/index/show_file/file_id/NDAyMzF4em9DdlRmdjJUZWZKamE0RHh3cVFrZkpVcHMvUkRSVElicC9OK0FuUzQ0U2YzcXpLclNGU3UxdzBDcGtDYnNzU1poU1QvWkt1ci9lQQ==" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">数据科学和大数据技术专业课程要求</a>和<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/general/index/show_file/file_id/YTEwNTNrSDV3bzlPcHR0ckgxUEphSk8yT1YrL2JCQ2NGTVBFcHhpL0dkbElCSk9iWGZBSmgweTcwTnhGaEpvRHg4cmh0em1ONWx4YzUrUmorQQ==" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">路径</a>。</li>
<li>智能制造专业课程要求：<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/general/index/show_file/file_id/MTFjYTJRa0NEMWZDZ1FRZ3YvaitLN3QxOWxnQnI4aXBqVWg2eGV0a3I3emFNcllPR2xWYitkRVdwZWUrZ2hLK2xKbU15NmxJOGpCSGRMWWxodw==" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">智能制造专业课程要求</a>和<a href="https://vptlo.hkust-gz.edu.cn/general/index/show_file/file_id/ZDhkMVVkY1U0VkRsM1JGVnpJM3ArK2xGKzR4SGVmZmhaVTREamZ1bWdyRXpHaHBGN0t4R1dpcUdYMjVyZFIxSnM5TTIrb2Npd1Vkam93dG5NUQ==" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">路径</a>。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="生活侧" tabindex="-1">生活侧 <a class="header-anchor" href="#生活侧" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;生活侧&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h3>
<ol>
<li><a href="https://pinbox.hkust-gz.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">校长信箱</a>。</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="学校架构" tabindex="-1">学校架构 <a class="header-anchor" href="#学校架构" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;学校架构&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<h2 id="学生侧活动" tabindex="-1">学生侧活动 <a class="header-anchor" href="#学生侧活动" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;学生侧活动&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<h2 id="注意事项" tabindex="-1">注意事项 <a class="header-anchor" href="#注意事项" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;注意事项&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ol>
<li>所有本科生必须在 5 月 31 日之前完成 CITI 研究诚信在线培训课程。</li>
</ol>
]]></content:encoded>
            <enclosure url="https://img2.imgtp.com/2024/05/16/cJLuw9ig.jpg" length="0" type="image/jpg"/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Web Design Resources]]></title>
            <link>undefined/posts/WebDesign</link>
            <guid>undefined/posts/WebDesign</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 12:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>下面给出一些可能的有用的素材和网站。</p>
<h2 id="图片和图标" tabindex="-1">图片和图标 <a class="header-anchor" href="#图片和图标" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;图片和图标&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://unsplash.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Unsplash</a> - 免费高质量的照片素材。</li>
<li><a href="https://www.flaticon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Flaticon</a> - 免费的矢量图标库。</li>
<li><a href="https://fontawesome.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">FontAwesome</a> - 开源的图标集合。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="颜色和配色方案" tabindex="-1">颜色和配色方案 <a class="header-anchor" href="#颜色和配色方案" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;颜色和配色方案&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://coolors.co/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Coolors</a> - 配色方案生成器。</li>
<li><a href="https://colorhunt.co/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Color Hunt</a> - 社区共享的配色方案。</li>
<li><a href="https://color.adobe.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Adobe Color</a> - Adobe 提供的配色工具。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="字体和排版" tabindex="-1">字体和排版 <a class="header-anchor" href="#字体和排版" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;字体和排版&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://fonts.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Google Fonts</a> - 免费的开源字体库。</li>
<li><a href="https://fonts.adobe.com/typekit" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Typekit</a> - Adobe 提供的高质量字体库。</li>
<li><a href="https://fontpair.co/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Font Pair</a> - 字体搭配推荐工具。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="设计工具" tabindex="-1">设计工具 <a class="header-anchor" href="#设计工具" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;设计工具&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.figma.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Figma</a> - 强大的在线设计工具。</li>
<li><a href="https://www.sketch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Sketch</a> - 专业的矢量设计工具。</li>
<li><a href="https://www.adobe.com/products/xd.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Adobe XD</a> - Adobe 提供的用户体验设计工具。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="学习资源" tabindex="-1">学习资源 <a class="header-anchor" href="#学习资源" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;学习资源&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">MDN Web Docs</a> - Web 技术文档和教程。</li>
<li><a href="https://css-tricks.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">CSS-Tricks</a> - CSS 相关的教程和技巧。</li>
<li><a href="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Smashing Magazine</a> - 设计和开发相关的文章和教程。</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded>
            <enclosure url="https://img2.imgtp.com/2024/05/16/siSQ05oz.jpg" length="0" type="image/jpg"/>
        </item>
